  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li> 5 Blueprint helper functions for multiplayer functional testing</li><li> 1 C&#43;&#43; helper function for multiplayer functional testing</li></ul><p>Number of Blueprints: 0</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 2</p><p>Network Replicated: No (The classes provided don&#39;t make sense to be replicated but they support replicated code)</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Win64</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Win64, Mac, Linux, Android, iOS</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/11Ss26q3j1IifSWYAvEY3mvNwl5BhD6egaciludfdg6Q/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Link</a></p><p>Example Project: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/11_H4YGAg27lA7eQNbg0kMvLpdDgIyY5R/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Link</a></p>",
